{"tid":2127522,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[客觀方析]其實武漢肺炎無想像中咁恐怖","createTime":"2020-07-27T11:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T18:13:11.000Z","uid":40757,"like":26,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"7731d182e25c7e2a162c65b22b05c2f2a55cb8a2","tid":2127522,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:12:41.000Z","msg":"Tldr:<br />\n當初呢個武漢病毒爆發既時候，因為香港以往SARS既慘痛經驗<br />\n、漢武大爆發既情況、對支那既不信任、外國既情況，從而overrated呢個病。<br />\n<br />\n但對於香港既情況，其實睇返數據，個病係比較影響有長者病患既長者；對非長者/ 身體免疫系統正常既人影響較輕。好多個案都係無病徵／輕微病徵既情況下好返出院。<br />\n<br />\n而呢隻武漢病毒作為單鏈既RNA病毒，本身就係好容易病變。但作為一隻病毒，最理想既情況係高傳染性、輕微病徵、低致死率，就同你玩Plague Inc.既情況差唔多，但少左最尾殺死哂全球人類呢步。因為佢需要宿主先可以「生存」，佢殺死你佢都「生存」唔到。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個病毒未來可能會傳染更多既人，但係好多都係無咩病徵、甚至係唔覺自己中左招，慢慢演變成風土病，或者好似流感咁，每年有個peak走出黎殺下一啲免疫力極低既人。<br />\n<br />\n最後，其實大家戴好口罩、自律咁減少出席人群聚集既場合，其實就算中左招都唔會咁易有事。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>睇返香港既死亡、危殆、嚴重個案：</ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong>死亡既暫時有19宗:</strong><br />\n<br />\n#13 (死亡) 39 歲 男<br />\n有長期病患的男患者居於黃埔花園 11 期 1 座。1 月 21 日曾乘搭高鐵到武漢探親<br />\n<br />\n#55 (死亡) 70 歲 男<br />\n#89 (死亡) 80 歲 男<br />\n#99 (死亡) 76 歲 女<br />\n#1092 (死亡) 78 歲 女<br />\n#1100 (死亡) 72 歲 男<br />\n<br />\n#1180 (死亡) 55 歲 男<br />\n患者於 2019 年 8 月到菲律賓，5 月底因中風入住當地醫院，6 月 13 日出現發燒症狀<br />\n<br />\n#1338 (死亡) 74 歲 男<br />\n#1341 (死亡) 95 歲 女<br />\n#1348 (死亡) 87 歲 男<br />\n#1350 (死亡) 90 歲 女<br />\n#1365 (死亡) 94 歲 男<br />\n#1450 (死亡) 89 歲 男<br />\n#1562 (死亡) 77 歲 男<span class=\"x-small\"></span><br />\n#1640 (死亡) 63 歲 男<br />\n#1707 (死亡) 71 歲 女<br />\n#1710 (死亡) 84 歲 男<br />\n#2480 (死亡) 60 歲 男<br />\n#2107 (死亡) 76 歲 女<br />\n#1306 (死亡) 92 歲 男<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">死亡個案得兩單係60歲以下，仲要本身長期病患<br />\n70歲以下都係得2單<br />\n<br />\n<strong>危殆有39宗</strong>:<br />\n年齡由52歲起跳<br />\n5個60歲以下(52,56,56,57,58)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>嚴重有25宗:</strong><br />\n一個26歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個50, 一個55<br />\n其他全部60歲或以上</span><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://wars.vote4.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpSwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=8b6fccd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://wars.vote4.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n剩餘既大部分好多都係asymptomatic/ mild symptom，一係唔使食藥好返；一係食下止痛消炎藥relief symptoms，唔使點治療既情況下就出得院<br />\n<br />\n我地再睇返張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9kxUJHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kxUJHq.jpg&h=1e834bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己思考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>我地再睇下外國數據</ins><br />\nAccording to the World Health Organization, about 20% of the cases may develop serious illness with breathing difficulty.<br />\n<br />\n40% of People With COVID-19 Show No Symptoms, The CDC Estimates<br />\n<br />\nResearchers say anywhere from 25 percent to 80 percent of people with COVID-19 are unaware they have the virus.<br />\n<br />\n(given that 鬼佬大把人唔戴罩)<br />\n而病情既嚴重程度同病毒既吸入量有一定關係<br />\n戴口罩可以阻隔一部分既病毒，從而減低病毒吸入量<br />\n係香港基本上9成以上既人都自律咁帶口罩，情況會更好。<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe17cbcd4cc31f8a9e105e91ff2d0a7616af279b","tid":2127522,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"你去奶扶手囉"},{"pid":"5e68cc0254a1c13f4083fadf3b07e8996ea53311","tid":2127522,"uid":30604,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:14:41.000Z","msg":"所以我長期唔戴罩 日日都落街跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e35bfda867be4e92db07f21cf88579cc612d462","tid":2127522,"uid":40757,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，今年2月至5月在各出入境管制站，向獲豁免進行14天強制檢疫人士，發出超過20萬張醫學監察通知書。<br />\n<br />\n議會陣線立法會議員毛孟靜關注，自抵港人士必須接受強制檢疫14天的規例實施以來，<span class=\"red\">每月有多少來自內地、澳門及台灣的人士，獲豁免遵守有關規定。</span><br />\n<br />\n保安局書面答覆指出，<span class=\"red\">今年2月共發出93602張醫學監察通知書、3月發出39211張、4月發出36039張，5月發出40220張。</span><br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，根據規例，<span class=\"red\">獲豁免進行14天強制檢疫人士，在留港期間要進行14天醫學監察，須戴口罩和每天量度體溫兩次，如有不適應向衞生署呈報。</span>有關人士在入境時，均須通過衞生署在<span class=\"red\">口岸進行的體溫監測和健康申報程序</span>。<br />\n<br />\n根源係冇封關免檢疫<br />\n就算香港禁足<br />\n全香港市民係屋企光合作用<br />\n但支那人繼續一車車咁入黎播毒<br />\n根本於事無補<br />\n<br />\n就好似之前有人講過咁<br />\n屋企水喉爆左，一直拖地但唔關水制，係永遠解決唔到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536645-20200708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536645-20200708.htm&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpSwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=f56bbe78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536645-20200708.htm&h=b01389d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536645-20200708.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8ca2a406b629afe3bf6f1962955a4a95043c17e5","tid":2127522,"uid":363990,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:17:57.000Z","msg":"你夠唔夠膽除罩係慈雲山行個圈？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ffa3771fefc04e1dd57f53d869b9b1e762cbc4","tid":2127522,"uid":40757,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"fe17cbcd4cc31f8a9e105e91ff2d0a7616af279b","tid":2127522,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"你去奶扶手囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而病情既嚴重程度同病毒既吸入量有一定關係<br />\n戴口罩可以阻隔一部分既病毒，從而減低病毒吸入量</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>最後，其實大家戴好口罩、自律咁減少出席人群聚集既場合，其實就算中左招都唔會咁易有事。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望你可以睇哂先至討論<br />\n唔係一味叫人奶乜奶物、或者叫我咁叻唔好戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n就算係傷風感冒，唔嚴重既病，唔代表想中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2722f574a20c0896fbe049149446e6a17809395e","tid":2127522,"uid":40757,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5e68cc0254a1c13f4083fadf3b07e8996ea53311","tid":2127522,"uid":30604,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:14:41.000Z","msg":"所以我長期唔戴罩 日日都落街跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6245ba90db80fccd5d72d65fbd8b0bed5c7ee3c","tid":2127522,"uid":169195,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"明明廢老傷D, 都唔友佢爆"},{"pid":"376495d793de069ccc9ea14fc04f9a864e562511","tid":2127522,"uid":361643,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"fe17cbcd4cc31f8a9e105e91ff2d0a7616af279b","tid":2127522,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"你去奶扶手囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:22:14.000Z","msg":"嚴唔嚴重同作死係兩回事 收番埋啲藍絲思維"},{"pid":"173cca01d5814818311ad395c437dc6f486ae3d8","tid":2127522,"uid":40757,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"8ca2a406b629afe3bf6f1962955a4a95043c17e5","tid":2127522,"uid":363990,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:17:57.000Z","msg":"你夠唔夠膽除罩係慈雲山行個圈？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"冇必要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有呼籲大家戴好口罩、自律咁減少出席人群聚集既場合<br />\n但無必要恐慌<br />\n<br />\n就算係傷風感冒咁輕微既病，都冇人會主動想要（唔計你想射波唔返工）"},{"pid":"14c016b58448691bb801ac8ce43beab323447a69","tid":2127522,"uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"樓主假兩難<br />\n唔係唔死就叫無事"},{"pid":"eeb9b6f922348332d334a00feb60d469fba5ee12","tid":2127522,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"後遺症呢？"},{"pid":"9f336d36abe680e5f052d049c803c51744bfb985","tid":2127522,"uid":40757,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c6245ba90db80fccd5d72d65fbd8b0bed5c7ee3c","tid":2127522,"uid":169195,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"明明廢老傷D, 都唔友佢爆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"爆唔爆唔係我決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係客觀指出個病冇大家想像中咁恐怖"},{"pid":"4e7966625dcb0f2158c0c06df2abe215853e95f4","tid":2127522,"uid":8109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"後生嘅其實無需過份恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做好基本嘅防疫工作就得<br />\n(長期病患除外）"},{"pid":"0164d4bd35005d719b7ab231efbd460f2d550d30","tid":2127522,"uid":40757,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14c016b58448691bb801ac8ce43beab323447a69","tid":2127522,"uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"樓主假兩難<br />\n唔係唔死就叫無事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"中咗武漢肺炎 你問我答<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aAfCnAU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aAfCnAU</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然連登仔講野不可盡信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但可以參考下"},{"pid":"afac6e63599a312879908094703ae32e5d176fc0","tid":2127522,"uid":33437,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"暫時醫療系統未超出負荷，<br />\n所以死亡率先低。"},{"pid":"ec0aade62af3b5993a0a6c743919ab8ee178e608","tid":2127522,"uid":186174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:26:26.000Z","msg":"信政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203184ea133437f9b3bf6ebf054f1415b6917a02","tid":2127522,"uid":27591,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:26:29.000Z","msg":"樓主應該係開餐廳"},{"pid":"9bd088e9181bc13179917bd3f350735392a1c040","tid":2127522,"uid":40757,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eeb9b6f922348332d334a00feb60d469fba5ee12","tid":2127522,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"後遺症呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:29:05.000Z","msg":"呢樣應該要睇個病既嚴重程度<br />\n好嚴重果D先會有肺花等後遺症<br />\n沙士有骨枯都係因為隻藥既問題<br />\n<br />\n但依家好多個案都係輕微，唔使食藥就出院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢班理論上應該唔會有咩嚴重既後遺症<br />\n<br />\n至於嚴重果班、食堆新藥果班<br />\n黎緊之後有冇啲咩好嚴重既後遺<br />\n我真係答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fdc2acdd45adffee8c8a9f5dadc6d85553e3fa","tid":2127522,"uid":158974,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"其實樓主講得好有道理，班二元對立撚做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心理上唔好恐慌同做好防護措施根本冇衝突"},{"pid":"5692704455ee56ce5209cd077d3cd66a7f7491c6","tid":2127522,"uid":181527,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"如果單憑死亡率去睇隻病係唔危險<br />\n但奶左野就算死唔去<br />\n個肺都爛晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9af01e968a791a27b66ea53394485059aac630","tid":2127522,"uid":40757,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"203184ea133437f9b3bf6ebf054f1415b6917a02","tid":2127522,"uid":27591,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:26:29.000Z","msg":"樓主應該係開餐廳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:30:38.000Z","msg":"我開餐廳／做飲食業<br />\n依家應該哭撚左<br />\n冇心情係到同你長篇大論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a47354250f83e0976eaabb92cb4973eeaae7ca","tid":2127522,"uid":177578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe17cbcd4cc31f8a9e105e91ff2d0a7616af279b","tid":2127522,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"你去奶扶手囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"啲pr/5毛真係好仆街<br />\n叫佢唔好帶口罩就扮睇唔到"},{"pid":"41c54c1085945480a30a5c88b2c5eb140c01a3ad"