g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b998d6ec52f3ac7aaceae881c7a1ff34432af21e","tid":2127522,"uid":28245,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:58:58.000Z","msg":"係連登講客觀分析 咪晒心機<br />\n<br />\n呢度唔係討論區<br />\n<br />\n一班鳩毛都未出齊既連衛兵渣旗<br />\n<br />\n非主流就係pr 5毛 <br />\n<br />\n極不理性無限上綱上線<br />\n<br />\n你比咁多分析 換黎只係奶扶手 pr 五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790fda8247d1d346e22c5d0acdd08ffe14b6df87","tid":2127522,"uid":149566,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1fvxRg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1fvxRg.png&h=d3aef160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明白樓主本意 有提唔封關做乜都冇用<br />\n但唔好叫人輕視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0c0a1d7a425a218502b366f1ae35ee66dbb271","tid":2127522,"uid":34899,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"理性之言<br />\n可惜香港人被蒙蔽雙眼"},{"pid":"fa2f0f9e9f80b771176b6948f33d0be8fe3f0483","tid":2127522,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:19:14.000Z","msg":"你只係建基於個病毒唔會變種黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一變種就仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}